Asserting with Testify     Go ships with a bare bones testing framwork, which coming from more feature complete testing platforms is a bit of a shock. Luckily the community provides!
go get &quot;github.com/stretchr/testify/assert&quot;
 assert.Equal()will do a deep equal powered by reflect.DeepEqualif given two structs. Do not roll out your own unless you have to!
